<item>
            <title>[LU-9719] readcache_max_filesize?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9719</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I want to verify that &#160;readcache_max_filesize is object size on OST not actual file size.&lt;/p&gt;

